Customer: Hello?

Executive: Haan.

Customer: Hello, good morning ma'am, IndiaMART se baat kar rahi thi. Ma'am aapne Nagma Begum ko call kiya tha?

Customer: Kiya tha but wo unko nahi chahiye service bola. Mujhe requirement nahi hai bola. Nagma Begum.

Executive: Haan.

Customer: Mat matlab requirement nahi hai, mai samjhi nahi aapki baat mein.

Customer: Matlab abhi jaise ki maine inquiry dali toh aapko samajh mein aaya, barabar?

Executive: Ji.

Customer: Toh wo kya bol rahi ki nahi mai aise kuch dekh hi nahi hu aise boli.

Executive: Just a second ma'am.







































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































OK ma'am. Actually hum aap close kar rahe the toh that's why I'm asking. Thank you ma'am.

Customer: Hello.
